# Publisher guardrails

- `wiki_vault/content` is the only publishable source of truth.
- Always sync `wiki_vault/content` into `publisher/quartz/content` before build.
- Build output must land in `/app/site` (or configured site dir) and be served by FastAPI.
- Preserve `content/attachments` during sync so asset links stay resolvable.
- In dev mode, support automatic rebuild on content changes.
- In prod mode, build on startup and rebuild only via explicit ingest/rebuild actions.
